export default function Lessons() { return (

In 9 Lessons we will look at the Book of Revelation divided into 22 (A-V) parts.

(A) Introduction [1:1-]

(B) Christ and the 7 Golden Candlesticks [1:]

(C) 7 Letters to 7 Churches [2-3]

(D) Vision of the Throne [4]

(E) Seven Seals [5-6; 8:1]

(G) 144,000 [7]

Lesson #5 [8:2-13; 9-11]:

(I) 7 Angels and 7 Trumpets [8:2-13; 9-10; 11:14-19]

(J) Measure the Temple of God [11:1,2]

(K) 2 Witnesses [11:3-13]

Lesson #6 [12-13]:

(L) Sun-clothed Woman

(M) 2 Beasts and the Dragon

Lesson #7 [14-18]:

(N) A Lamb Stood on Mount Sion

(O) Judgement Hour Messages

(P) 7 Last Plagues in Vials

(Q) Fall of Babylon

Lesson #8 [19-20]:

(R) The Marriage and Marriage Feast of the Lamb

(S) Millenial Kingdom

(T) Last Judgment

Lesson #9 [21-22]:

(U) All Things New

(V) Closing

) }
